@node "install" "Install"

 Just copy @{b}MATRIX HUNTER@{ub} the disk to your harddrive or leave it on a disk,
 but don't protect the disk for writing on it !
 To start the game just click the MATRIX HUNTER-Icon - that's all.


@endnode




@node "usage" "usage"

 @{u}@{b}How to play MATRIX HUNTER@{ub}@{uu}

 After starting @{b}MATRIX HUNTER@{ub} with a doubleclick at the Icon,
 you will see the gametitle and some animations. Press "ESC"- to exit 
 the game and press "FIRE" to start.
 
 You will find your base in the middle of a matrix. With the Joystick you
 set the direction of your fire. The station will automaticly turn in to the
 right direction.
 Now shoot all enemys down before they hit or shoot you!

 Pressing the "SPACE"-bar will detonate a super-bomb (you have 5 of them).
 The Super-bomb kills every ship and the bullets of them !

 
 You can always exit the game by pressing "ESC" or pause the game with "P"

  
 To EXIT THE GAME press during the titlesequence  "ESC".
 The hi-score-list and game-config will be saved !
        

